                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8558" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1307</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1531 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术驱动数字化交互平台：禾乡农场“认养一头猪”项目多方共赢的背后故事</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Technology Motivate Digital Interactive Platform: A Win-win Story behind the “Adopt a Pig” Project of HEXIANG Farm </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">戴鑫，但昭杰，舒家祺，胡诗珮，郭一</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新灵境科技研究（海南）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化交互平台；认养农业；消费者体验；参与者交互；感知价值；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digitalized Interactive Platform, Adopt Farm, Consumer Experience, Participant Interaction, Perceived Value</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化交互平台，一般是指将产品移植为数字化形式，并加入各部分参与者、各种流程和界面的营销互动体系。2021年以来，赵国君与合伙人们一起返乡创立“禾乡农场”，运用数字技术驱动农业发展，实现助农增收。平台上线前，项目创始人们创新性地采用新认养农业模式，通过物联网技术，解决农户、用户双方对企业的不信任问题；平台运营中，项目创始人们通过人工智能、区块链技术帮助农户摒弃陈旧养猪观念，帮助用户解决产品储存难的问题；平台成熟后，禾乡农场与五峰县政府积极合作，完善配套设施建设，助力乡村振兴。目前，禾乡农场平台正稳步发展；未来，合伙人们期望运用更多数字技术，建立真正意义上的数字农场。本案例从数字化交互平台视角出发，讲述了禾乡农场项目成员如何利用数字技术驱动认养农业发展，提升消费者参与体验，实现多方共赢的故事。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Digitalized interactive platform, generally refers to the transplantation of products into digital form, and join the various parts of the participants, a variety of processes and interfaces of the interactive system of marketing. 2021, Zhao Guojun and his partners returned to their hometowns to create the &quot;HEXIANG Farm&quot;, using digital technology to drive agricultural development. Before the platform was launched, the founders of the project innovatively adopted the new agriculture model, through the Internet of Things technology, to solve the problem of farmers and users of the enterprise&#39;s mistrust. During the platform operation, the founders of the project, through artificial intelligence, blockchain technology to help farmers abandon stereotypical pig farming concepts, to help users solving the problem of difficult to store the product. After the platform going maturity, HEXIANG Farm and Wufeng County Government actively cooperate to improve the supporting facilities construction, to help rural revitalization and to facilitate construction. At present, HEXIANG Farm&#39;s platform is developing steadily. In the future, the partners expect to use more digital technologies and establish a digital farm in the true sense. From the perspective of a digitalized interactive platform, this case tells the story of how HEXIANG Farm project members used digital technology to drive the development of subscription agriculture, enhance the consumer experience and realize a win-win situation for all parties.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《数字营销》、《新媒体营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化交互平台以及数智化营销相关理论（数字化交互平台的内涵、运作机制，数字化交互平台的定义、营销要素、参与者交互机制、参与者交互的营销机制、在线运行机制、在线运行的营销机制以及发展趋势）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
